														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-456424">
									

<p>Can you imagine what would happen if this thing got out without a proper vaccine? With such a high infection rate, it might lead to the end of modern society! Imagine a world where nobody could count! So many things would fall apart that we'd be blasted back to the Stone Age. No ability to judge proportions, no ability to handle sets of objects…</p>
<p>Since the symptoms take time to develop, as well as being relatively hidden, lots of people would catch the virus before they knew of its effects. This might help the virus spread until quarantine becomes ineffective.</p>
<p>The article notes that ninety percent of non-immune people will contract the disease within thirty days; I'm not entirely sure where they would get their immunity from, given that the article also declares the standard measles vaccine ineffective. Does innate measles resistance also protect against SCP-593? If so, this gets a bit less scary.</p>

